high_descs: Turn left to walk down the passage and take a right turn to enter the room with a brown shelf.
Pick up the brown statue from the floor.
Put the statue in the second shelf from the left and the bottom.
Pick up the black statue from the floor.
Put it next to the brown statue in the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put two statues in the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and go in front of the room with statue
Enter the room and go in front of the rack
Pick up the statue lying on the floor
Lift the statue and bring to left rack
Keep the statue on the second rack from floor near the corner
anns.task_desc: Go to the room with racks and keep the statue fell on the floor to rack on the left.

high_descs: Turn to your left, move straight, now turn to your right, go straight, then turn to your left facing the shelf
Pick the brown statue on the floor
Put in the wooden shelf
Pick up the black statue on the floor
Put it next to the wooden shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the statues in the shelf

high_descs: go into the door for the statue
pick up the statue from the floor
Set the statue on the shelf to your left.
pick up another statue from the floor
Set the statue on the shelf to your left next to the other.
anns.task_desc: Pick up statues from the floor and set on the shelf

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the statue in the store room and turn right.
Enter to the store and walk few steps straight to the statue.
Turn slightly left and slightly right and take the statue from the shelf.
Place the statue on the Wooden rack.
Take the second statue and place it on the same shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the two statue on the wooden shelf.

high_descs: Exit from the room, go straight, turn left, then turn right, and reach the statue on the wooden rack.
collect the statue to bottom of the rack
Take the statue inside the wooden shelf on toy.
Again collect the statue.
Collect the statue from the wooden shelf and put it on the cupboard.
anns.task_desc: Collect the statue from wooden shelf and put it on the cupboard.
